    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, and the braking system retains excellent bite with minimal fade. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. This is a high-performance specimen optimized for tactile feedback and longitudinal grip.",
