      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV represents the perfect balance of rugged capability and refined comfort. Finished in a deep Midnight Black Metallic, the exterior retains a high-gloss luster, showing only the minor road-wear consistent with careful highway use. Step inside to a spacious cabin where the premium leather seating remains supple and supportive, featuring only light character creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every amenity, from the multi-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves its mechanical integrity. The undercarriage is clean, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garage-kept and professionally detailed. It offers the peace of mind of a reliable daily driver with the incredible value of a well-cared-for pre-owned gem, ready for its next long-distance adventure.",
